ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 191, Saskatchewan
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 191 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of SASKATCHEWAN, with respect to the SEVERE FLOODING, that affected the province, from April 7, 2014 to May 5, 2014.
